title: Young Irishman dies in San Francisco
text:
Young Irishman dies in San Francisco 
Irish Examiner Saturday 24th October, 2015 
A 23-year old Irishman has died in San Francisco, California, it has emerged tonight.Dean MacCeara?n, from Co Monaghan, is thought to have travelled to the US to attend his brother's wedding.The Department of Foreign Affairs is providing consular assistance to his family.The cause of his death is not yet known.
